Privacy Policy for Rental House Market Scraper
Last Updated: April 22, 2025

Thank you for using Rental House Market Scraper ("the App"), a web scraping tool developed by [Your Company/Name] ("we," "us," or "our"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use the App.

1. Information We Collect
Your Inputs: URLs or search terms you provide to scrape rental housing data.
Usage Data: How you use the App, like features accessed or websites scraped.
Device Info: IP address, browser type, or device details.
Scraped Data: Publicly available rental data processed temporarily to deliver results.

2. How We Use Your Information
We use your information to:
Run the App and deliver scraping results.
Improve the App’s performance.
Respond to your inquiries or provide support.

3. Sharing Your Information
We don’t sell your information. We may share it with:
Service providers helping run the App (e.g., cloud storage), under strict confidentiality.
Authorities, if required by law.

4. Scraped Data
You’re responsible for ensuring your scraping complies with laws and website terms. We don’t store scraped data unless you ask us to, and you must have the legal right to collect it.

5. Data Security
We take reasonable steps to protect your information, but no system is 100% secure. We keep your data only as long as needed.

6. Your Rights
You may request to access, correct, or delete your information by contacting us at [Your Contact Email]. You can stop using the App anytime.

7. Third-Party Sites
The App scrapes third-party websites, which have their own privacy policies. We’re not responsible for their practices.

8. Changes
We may update this policy and will notify you of major changes. Continued use means you accept the updates.
